language Essence 1.3

given g: int(1..)
given s: int(1..)
given w: int(1..)
letting n be g * s
find schedule: matrix indexed by [int(1..w), int(1..n)] of int(1..g)
such that
    and([and([sum([toInt(schedule[week, player] = grp) | player : int(1..n)]) = s | grp : int(1..g)])
             | week : int(1..w)]),
    and([and([and([p1 < p2 -> !(schedule[w1, p1] = schedule[w1, p2] /\ schedule[w2, p1] = schedule[w2, p2])
                       | p1 : int(1..n), p2 : int(1..n)])
                  | w2 : int(w1 + 1..w)])
             | w1 : int(1..w)])

